examples.en: Bob reversed into a parking space.
I reversed the car into a side road.
The decision was reversed on appeal.
The verdict was reversed by a superior court.
The reversed collar looked as good as new.
The court reversed the lower court's decision.
The runners reversed their direction on the track.
Our roles as child and guardian had now been reversed.
He reversed short positions and went long on Hong Kong stocks.
My mother and I reversed our roles. Now I'm taking care of her.
The dance teacher had to keep reminding us to kick our hindmost foot when we reversed direction.
